Company Description                    




                        Thai Vegetable Oil PCL produces and distributes cooking oil. The company also distributes ground soy beans. The product includes sunflower oil, sunflower meal, soybean oil, full fat soy, and lecithin. The company was established in 1985 and is based in Bangkok, Thailand.                    


