TOP Nautical Star Company Limited (TOP-NS)







TOP-NS is registered in Thailand as a  company under the Thaioil Marine group which provides storage and transportation services for crude oil, feedstock, and petroleum products.



Commencement of Commercial Operation
2013


Business Type
Transport crude oil, feedstock and petroleum products by large ship.


Capacity
2 AFRAMAX ships (a combined 202,290 dead weight ton capacity)


Products / Services
